- whoever scores this point
- Good, good.

576
00:27:40,460 --> 00:27:42,280
wins the match.

577
00:27:46,060 --> 00:27:46,960
She's amazing.

578
00:27:49,000 --> 00:27:50,360
Still thinking about praising others?

579
00:27:51,860 --> 00:27:53,280
Didn't you see the ball coming right at you?

580
00:27:53,820 --> 00:27:54,900
Why don't you work on your fitness

581
00:27:54,900 --> 00:27:55,740
a bit more?

582
00:27:57,340 --> 00:27:58,840
I know that's my weak spot.

583
00:28:06,540 --> 00:28:08,440
What? You hit me earlier.

584
00:28:08,820 --> 00:28:09,660
We're even now.

585
00:28:11,620 --> 00:28:12,840
You only scored one point.

586
00:28:13,220 --> 00:28:14,060
Don't be smug.

587
00:28:14,900 --> 00:28:15,740
A sore loser?

588
00:28:16,220 --> 00:28:17,240
I didn't even ask you to apologize.

589
00:28:17,540 --> 00:28:18,440
I'm a sore loser?

590
00:28:19,220 --> 00:28:20,240
I'm not like some people

591
00:28:20,940 --> 00:28:21,800
who won the match

592
00:28:22,020 --> 00:28:23,280
but lost the most important thing.

593
00:28:31,260 --> 00:28:34,460
(Beach Volleyball Challenge)

594
00:28:38,300 --> 00:28:39,140
Gao.

595
00:28:40,140 --> 00:28:41,580
Didn't you say you couldn't play?

596
00:28:41,580 --> 00:28:42,420
You played really well.

597
00:28:42,630 --> 00:28:43,600
I really can't play.

598
00:28:43,860 --> 00:28:45,440
Champion and runner-up,
let's go get our awards.

599
00:28:46,060 --> 00:28:47,280
Congratulations, you're the champion.

600
00:28:47,420 --> 00:28:48,260
Hurry and get your award.

601
00:28:48,980 --> 00:28:50,260
Champion! Champion! Come here.

602
00:28:50,260 --> 00:28:51,100
This way, this way.

603
00:28:51,500 --> 00:28:52,340
To the podium.

604
00:28:52,780 --> 00:28:53,820
- Let's go.
- This way.

605
00:28:53,820 --> 00:28:54,840
My granddaughter is here.

606
00:28:56,420 --> 00:28:57,260
Great, great.

607
00:28:59,220 --> 00:29:00,240
Amazing.

608
00:29:00,820 --> 00:29:01,660
Weilan.

609
00:29:01,700 --> 00:29:02,540
You played so well,

610
00:29:02,740 --> 00:29:04,140
especially that last shot.

611
00:29:04,140 --> 00:29:05,660
Smack! It was awesome.

612
00:29:05,660 --> 00:29:07,460
I felt like I couldn't jump

613
00:29:07,460 --> 00:29:08,700
in the sand.

614
00:29:08,700 --> 00:29:09,900
And the wind direction.

615
00:29:09,900 --> 00:29:10,740
I couldn't get it right.

616
00:29:11,380 --> 00:29:12,820
Playing on sand

617
00:29:12,820 --> 00:29:13,900
is definitely different

618
00:29:13,900 --> 00:29:15,000
from playing indoors.

619
00:29:15,300 --> 00:29:16,660
It's okay. Take it slow.

620
00:29:16,660 --> 00:29:17,820
You'll adapt slowly.

621
00:29:17,820 --> 00:29:18,660
Right?

622
00:29:18,820 --> 00:29:19,660
Mainly,

623
00:29:19,660 --> 00:29:21,780
you two coordinated really well today.

624
00:29:21,780 --> 00:29:22,620
You know that?

625
00:29:23,780 --> 00:29:25,660
Grandpa rarely praises me.

626
00:29:25,660 --> 00:29:27,540
My granddaughter is the best.

627
00:29:27,540 --> 00:29:28,640
Of course, I praise you.

628
00:29:28,700 --> 00:29:30,700
(Jin Yun Hotel Opening Ceremony
Beach Volleyball Challenge)

629
00:29:30,700 --> 00:29:32,140
Let's welcome our champions

630
00:29:32,140 --> 00:29:33,140
to the stage

631
00:29:33,140 --> 00:29:34,120
for the ceremony.

632
00:29:34,700 --> 00:29:36,380
Next,

633
00:29:36,380 --> 00:29:38,300
let's welcome our award presenters,

634
00:29:38,300 --> 00:29:39,700
Mr. Wang and Mr. Zhang.

635
00:29:39,700 --> 00:29:40,940
Please present the flowers

636
00:29:40,940 --> 00:29:42,060
and the prize money

637
00:29:42,060 --> 00:29:43,140
to our champions.

638
00:29:43,140 --> 00:29:43,980
A round of applause!

639
00:29:45,060 --> 00:29:46,300
- Congratulations!
- Congratulations!

640
00:29:46,300 --> 00:29:48,050
(A check for ten thousand yuan)
Here. Congratulations.

641
00:29:48,050 --> 00:29:49,580
- Thank you.
- Congratulations, congratulations.

642
00:29:49,580 --> 00:29:49,890
Thank you.

643
00:29:49,890 --> 00:29:51,660
Let's have our award presenters

644
00:29:51,660 --> 00:29:53,560
and our champion take a group photo.

645
00:29:53,780 --> 00:29:56,020
Alright, everyone can take photos now.

646
00:29:56,020 --> 00:29:57,080
At this time,

647
00:29:57,300 --> 00:29:58,740
our journalist

648
00:29:58,740 --> 00:29:59,900
can conduct interviews.

649
00:29:59,900 --> 00:30:01,320
Come forward, come forward.

650
00:30:05,660 --> 00:30:07,240
Did I play poorly today?

651
00:30:08,140 --> 00:30:09,020
I feel like Gao Ge

652
00:30:09,020 --> 00:30:10,560
might be a bit disappointed with me.

653
00:30:11,220 --> 00:30:12,060
No.

654
00:30:12,340 --> 00:30:13,620
Gao is just like that.

655
00:30:13,620 --> 00:30:14,460
Don't take it to heart.

656
00:30:15,660 --> 00:30:17,800
But I really didn't play well.

657
00:30:18,500 --> 00:30:20,320
Even Tu Lingling said my strength isn't enough.

658
00:30:20,540 --> 00:30:21,380
But

659
00:30:22,140 --> 00:30:24,360
playing face-to-face with Chen Weilan today,

660
00:30:24,820 --> 00:30:26,560
I really think she's impressive.

661
00:30:27,340 --> 00:30:28,660
She plays indoor volleyball.

662
00:30:28,660 --> 00:30:30,000
She's never played beach volleyball before.

663
00:30:30,380 --> 00:30:31,660
The court was unfamiliar

664
00:30:31,660 --> 00:30:32,700
to her,

665
00:30:32,700 --> 00:30:33,800
yet she played so well.

666
00:30:35,300 --> 00:30:36,420
I'm really

667
00:30:36,420 --> 00:30:37,580
thousands of miles behind her.

668
00:30:38,260 --> 00:30:39,940
Not thousands of miles behind.

669
00:30:39,940 --> 00:30:40,790
Maybe just three or four miles.

670
00:30:42,060 --> 00:30:42,900
After all,

671
00:30:43,100 --> 00:30:44,780
geniuses are rare.

672
00:30:44,780 --> 00:30:45,980
Don't be discouraged.

673
00:30:45,980 --> 00:30:47,220
With your current effort,

674
00:30:47,220 --> 00:30:48,800
you'll be just as good in the future.

675
00:30:50,940 --> 00:30:52,800
Sure. I rise to the challenge.

676
00:30:53,300 --> 00:30:54,380
Once I enter university,

677
00:30:54,380 --> 00:30:55,280
I'll work even harder.

678
00:30:59,540 --> 00:31:00,380
What's wrong?

679
00:31:03,060 --> 00:31:05,120
I still haven't settled my university tuition.

680
00:31:10,580 --> 00:31:11,720
Did you forget about that?

681
00:31:14,540 --> 00:31:15,380
That's not right.

682
00:31:15,380 --> 00:31:16,540
This is the prize money you won.

683
00:31:16,540 --> 00:31:17,700
How can I take your money?

684
00:31:17,700 --> 00:31:18,620
Why not?

685
00:31:18,620 --> 00:31:19,740
It's the money you and Gao won.

686
00:31:19,740 --> 00:31:20,660
It's rightfully yours.

687
00:31:20,660 --> 00:31:22,580
Absolutely not. It's your money. I...

688
00:31:22,580 --> 00:31:23,420
How about this?

689
00:31:23,420 --> 00:31:25,340
Consider this money a loan from me.

690
00:31:25,340 --> 00:31:26,760
It's also with Chen Weilan's approval.

691
00:31:26,980 --> 00:31:28,920
And you have to write me an IOU.

692
00:31:39,620 --> 00:31:41,140
It's home at last.

693
00:31:41,140 --> 00:31:42,940
How long has it been since you visited me?

694
00:31:42,940 --> 00:31:44,380
The flowers in the yard are blooming.

695
00:31:44,380 --> 00:31:45,220
Yes.

696
00:31:46,660 --> 00:31:47,700
Come on.

697
00:31:47,700 --> 00:31:49,340
- Let me do it.
- It's fine.

698
00:31:49,340 --> 00:31:50,460
- Let me do it.
- I can handle it.

699
00:31:50,460 --> 00:31:51,780
- Really?
- I can handle it.

700
00:31:51,780 --> 00:31:52,780
I'll help you.

701
00:31:52,780 --> 00:31:53,800
I'm not that old.

702
00:31:54,140 --> 00:31:55,820
I can't let you get tired.

703
00:31:55,820 --> 00:31:56,660
Right?

704
00:31:56,820 --> 00:31:58,020
Then I'll open the door.

705
00:31:58,020 --> 00:31:58,860
Okay.

706
00:32:01,300 --> 00:32:03,040
Alright, we're home.

707
00:32:04,260 --> 00:32:05,640
Come in, come in.

708
00:32:06,740 --> 00:32:07,740
Weilan, look.

709
00:32:07,740 --> 00:32:09,580
Isn't your room decorated

710
00:32:09,580 --> 00:32:10,800
even more beautifully than before?

711
00:32:11,820 --> 00:32:12,920
Put it here.

712
00:32:14,020 --> 00:32:15,480
So many more photos now.

713
00:32:23,140 --> 00:32:24,600
So cozy.

714
00:32:26,460 --> 00:32:27,720
No way, Grandpa.

715
00:32:28,100 --> 00:32:31,220
You kept these certificates and trophies?

716
00:32:31,220 --> 00:32:32,820
Of course.

717
00:32:32,820 --> 00:32:33,960
They're the most important.

718
00:32:37,700 --> 00:32:38,980
Do you remember this?

719
00:32:38,980 --> 00:32:39,820
Look.

720
00:32:39,860 --> 00:32:41,400
(Certificate)
Chen Weilan.

721
00:32:42,300 --> 00:32:44,580
This was your first honor

722
00:32:44,580 --> 00:32:45,520
in beach volleyball.

723
00:32:46,100 --> 00:32:47,160
It's very precious.

724
00:32:50,580 --> 00:32:52,480
Time flies.

725
00:32:53,920 --> 00:32:55,820
In a blink, it's been over ten years.

726
00:32:55,940 --> 00:32:56,940
Back then,

727
00:32:56,940 --> 00:32:58,460
you were only six years old.

728
00:32:59,500 --> 00:33:00,340
This tall.

729
00:33:04,020 --> 00:33:05,920
My precious granddaughter.

730
00:33:06,460 --> 00:33:07,300
I know

731
00:33:07,780 --> 00:33:08,780
this time,

732
00:33:08,780 --> 00:33:09,740
you missed out

733
00:33:09,740 --> 00:33:10,680
on the National Youth Team,

734
00:33:11,220 --> 00:33:13,100
and didn't get into the Sports University.

735
00:33:13,100 --> 00:33:14,240
You must be feeling down.

736
00:33:15,060 --> 00:33:16,680
But I'm happy to see

737
00:33:16,980 --> 00:33:18,860
you're still pursuing

738
00:33:18,860 --> 00:33:19,800
your dreams.

739
00:33:20,500 --> 00:33:21,340
That's great.

740
00:33:22,300 --> 00:33:23,620
You're still young.

741
00:33:23,620 --> 00:33:25,320
As long as you persist, there's hope.

742
00:33:26,660 --> 00:33:27,500
Yes.

743
00:33:27,740 --> 00:33:29,140
I'm still persisting.

744
00:33:29,140 --> 00:33:30,380
I must keep playing volleyball.

745
00:33:30,380 --> 00:33:31,240
Of course.

746
00:33:32,220 --> 00:33:33,060
Which one?

747
00:33:34,500 --> 00:33:35,540
- This one.
- Check, please.

748
00:33:35,540 --> 00:33:36,380
- Okay.
- Coming.

749
00:33:36,380 --> 00:33:37,320
Help me with the check.

750
00:33:38,340 --> 00:33:39,760
- How many skewers?
- Eat while it's hot.

751
00:33:40,540 --> 00:33:41,380
Sure.

752
00:33:42,620 --> 00:33:44,200
- How about this?
- Sure.

753
00:33:44,700 --> 00:33:45,540
Alright.

754
00:33:45,740 --> 00:33:46,580
I'm back.

755
00:33:46,740 --> 00:33:47,580
Dad,

756
00:33:47,900 --> 00:33:49,280
you rest. I'll take over.

757
00:33:49,280 --> 00:33:50,120
Alright.

758
00:33:50,820 --> 00:33:51,660
It's 176 in total.

759
00:33:52,140 --> 00:33:52,980
Alright.

760
00:33:54,340 --> 00:33:55,180
Paid.

761
00:33:55,300 --> 00:33:56,210
- Okay.
- Take care.

762
00:33:57,620 --> 00:33:58,460
Dad,

763
00:33:58,740 --> 00:34:00,740
today you and Mom can close up early and rest.

764
00:34:00,740 --> 00:34:01,900
Lately, you can take it easy.

765
00:34:01,900 --> 00:34:02,740
No need to work so hard.

766
00:34:03,180 --> 00:34:04,220
Rest?

767
00:34:04,220 --> 00:34:05,160
Where will the tuition come from?

768
00:34:05,820 --> 00:34:07,400
I've earned my tuition.

769
00:34:08,180 --> 00:34:09,130
So, you and Mom

770
00:34:09,130 --> 00:34:10,440
don't have to work so hard anymore.

771
00:34:19,820 --> 00:34:21,040
Where did you get so much money?

772
00:34:21,740 --> 00:34:23,960
I won it in a beach volleyball match.

773
00:34:24,500 --> 00:34:25,460
So, you both

774
00:34:25,460 --> 00:34:26,300
can take it easy.

775
00:34:26,300 --> 00:34:27,640
No need to work from dawn to dusk.

776
00:34:27,980 --> 00:34:28,820
And this.

777
00:34:29,660 --> 00:34:31,380
They say this ointment works really well.

778
00:34:31,380 --> 00:34:32,960
Try it. You'll be comfortable at night.

779
00:34:33,860 --> 00:34:35,600
Such a good daughter we have.

780
00:34:36,420 --> 00:34:37,260
You are

781
00:34:37,610 --> 00:34:38,780
just like your mom,

782
00:34:38,780 --> 00:34:40,400
spending money recklessly when you have some.

783
00:34:41,500 --> 00:34:42,750
If you really care about me,

784
00:34:43,020 --> 00:34:44,710
study hard and find a good job.

785
00:34:46,050 --> 00:34:47,160
Got it.

786
00:34:51,610 --> 00:34:53,260
Two more beers, please.

787
00:34:53,260 --> 00:34:54,380
- Sure.
- Coming.

788
00:34:54,380 --> 00:34:55,220
Wait a moment.

789
00:34:55,220 --> 00:34:56,400
You put the money away. I'll go.

790
00:34:56,700 --> 00:34:57,540
Coming.

791
00:35:02,980 --> 00:35:04,180
Here are your beers.

792
00:35:04,180 --> 00:35:05,020
Thank you.

793
00:35:10,660 --> 00:35:12,460
(Beach Volleyball Practice Game
Sign up now)

794
00:35:14,180 --> 00:35:15,590
- Why don't you sign up?
- I should sign up too.

795
00:35:16,900 --> 00:35:17,740
Yeah.

796
00:35:18,030 --> 00:35:19,040
- Give it a try.
- Go and win the game.

797
00:35:24,020 --> 00:35:24,860
Wait a moment.

798
00:35:27,320 --> 00:35:28,160
Hello?

799
00:35:28,160 --> 00:35:29,060
Hey, Xia.

800
00:35:29,060 --> 00:35:29,900
Where are you?

801
00:35:30,340 --> 00:35:31,520
In the cafeteria. What's up?

802
00:35:31,780 --> 00:35:33,520
The province is organizing
a beach volleyball practice game.

803
00:35:33,780 --> 00:35:34,740
Let's find Coach Wang

804
00:35:34,740 --> 00:35:35,580
to sign us up.

805
00:35:35,860 --> 00:35:37,140
Sure, wait for me.

806
00:35:37,140 --> 00:35:38,100
Wait for me. I'm coming.

807
00:35:38,100 --> 00:35:39,020
Alright, you finish eating first.

808
00:35:39,020 --> 00:35:39,860
Don't forget.

809
00:35:48,140 --> 00:35:49,080
What's the rush?

810
00:35:51,820 --> 00:35:52,860
There's a competition soon.

811
00:35:52,860 --> 00:35:53,700
I'm going to sign up.

812
00:35:54,660 --> 00:35:56,060
You're in your fourth year.

813
00:35:56,060 --> 00:35:57,840
Focus on your future.

814
00:35:58,940 --> 00:35:59,780
Got it.

815
00:36:00,220 --> 00:36:01,080
Xia Liqiang,

816
00:36:07,580 --> 00:36:08,520
Jing,

817
00:36:08,940 --> 00:36:10,000
I'm off.

818
00:36:10,700 --> 00:36:11,540
Well.

819
00:36:12,460 --> 00:36:13,820
If you need anything, send me a WeChat message.

820
00:36:13,820 --> 00:36:14,960
I promise to reply immediately.

821
00:36:15,940 --> 00:36:16,880
Got it.

822
00:36:17,580 --> 00:36:18,420
Alright.

823
00:36:19,700 --> 00:36:20,540
Goodbye.

824
00:36:24,540 --> 00:36:25,380
(Xingang University)

825
00:36:25,380 --> 00:36:26,840
Coach, about the practice game...

826
00:36:28,660 --> 00:36:29,860
Gao Ge, look.

827
00:36:29,860 --> 00:36:31,280
You've made a lot of progress

828
00:36:31,980 --> 00:36:33,120
this semester training with me.

829
00:36:33,460 --> 00:36:34,300
Coach,

830
00:36:34,620 --> 00:36:36,300
you deserve some credit for that.

831
00:36:36,300 --> 00:36:37,560
But Gao has talent too.

832
00:36:38,020 --> 00:36:38,920
He does have talent.

833
00:36:40,060 --> 00:36:41,140
That's why I think

834
00:36:41,140 --> 00:36:42,180
such practice games

835
00:36:42,180 --> 00:36:43,020
aren't suitable for you.

836
00:36:44,380 --> 00:36:45,220
Coach,

837
00:36:45,460 --> 00:36:47,160
you can't stop us from competing.

838
00:36:47,420 --> 00:36:48,700
You didn't let us participate

839
00:36:48,700 --> 00:36:49,760
in last year's Seven-School League.

840
00:36:50,180 --> 00:36:51,020
I know.

841
00:36:51,220 --> 00:36:52,600
Last year, he was in his first year.

842
00:36:53,100 --> 00:36:54,760
It would have only hurt his confidence.

843
00:36:55,780 --> 00:36:56,620
Coach,

844
00:36:56,860 --> 00:36:58,220
that's water under the bridge.

845
00:36:58,220 --> 00:36:59,060
Forget about it.

846
00:36:59,420 --> 00:37:00,640
But this time, both Xia and I

847
00:37:01,130 --> 00:37:02,220
really want to participate

848
00:37:02,220 --> 00:37:03,530
in this practice game.

849
00:37:04,290 --> 00:37:06,420
Could you please support us?

850
00:37:07,060 --> 00:37:07,900
Sure.

851
00:37:08,220 --> 00:37:10,260
I'm your biggest supporter.

852
00:37:10,260 --> 00:37:11,100
Right?

853
00:37:11,900 --> 00:37:14,120
But still, like I said earlier.

854
00:37:14,860 --> 00:37:16,220
I don't think those competitions

855
00:37:16,220 --> 00:37:17,220
are right for you.

856
00:37:17,220 --> 00:37:18,240
Participating won't benefit you.

857
00:37:21,940 --> 00:37:22,780
But that's okay.

858
00:37:23,220 --> 00:37:24,880
I've arranged something for you.

859
00:37:25,940 --> 00:37:27,040
Go to the club and play some games,

860
00:37:27,780 --> 00:37:28,620
alright?

861
00:37:29,260 --> 00:37:30,480
There are top players there,

862
00:37:31,620 --> 00:37:33,380
which will be very helpful

863
00:37:33,380 --> 00:37:34,440
