901
00:38:48,340 --> 00:38:49,180
That's why

902
00:38:49,860 --> 00:38:51,220
Ocean University's beach volleyball team

903
00:38:51,220 --> 00:38:52,060
is thriving,

904
00:38:52,380 --> 00:38:54,240
