924
00:39:49,420 --> 00:39:50,700
Why should you, as students,

925
00:39:50,700 --> 00:39:52,140
play in clubs?

926
00:39:52,140 --> 00:39:53,120
Exactly.

927
00:39:54,300 --> 00:39:55,980
He insists we participate

928
