958
00:41:03,900 --> 00:41:04,940
I thought I'd come and ask

959
00:41:04,940 --> 00:41:06,360
if you could give him a chance.

960
00:41:10,260 --> 00:41:11,680
I've given him a chance.

961
00:41:12,340 --> 00:41:13,620
I've told him before

962
00:41:13,620 --> 00:41:15,220
