his coach's instructions.

978
00:41:40,460 --> 00:41:41,300
Alright.

979
00:41:41,860 --> 00:41:42,700
How about this?

980
00:41:43,300 --> 00:41:44,320
Go back and talk to him.

981
00:41:45,420 --> 00:41:46,800
Convince him to play at the club.

982
00:41:47,380 --> 00:41:48,220
Alright?

983
00:41:48,220 --> 00:41:49,070
If he can go,

984
00:41:49,660 --> 00:41:51,460
